New York City’s 311 program has six service request categories related to dog poop. They are:


Code
suppressMessages(dog_poop_sr &lt;- read_csv("dog_poop_SRs.csv"))

dog_poop_sr |&gt; 
  flextable() |&gt; 
  set_table_properties(width = 1, layout = "autofit") |&gt; 
  align(j = 1, align = "left", part = "all")


